Bundled third-party components
--------------------------------

Gorex distributes the following pre-built binaries as part of its release
packages. Each component retains its own license:

  HandBrake CLI (HandBrakeCLI.exe / HandBrakeCLI)
    License: GNU General Public License Version 2
    Source:  https://github.com/HandBrake/HandBrake

  yt-dlp (yt-dlp.exe / yt-dlp_macos)
    License: The Unlicense (public domain)
    Source:  https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp

  ffmpeg / ffprobe
    License: GNU Lesser General Public License Version 2.1 (or later)
    Source:  https://ffmpeg.org

Because Gorex bundles and distributes HandBrake CLI (GPLv2), the combined
distribution as a whole is subject to the terms of the GNU General Public
License Version 2. Gorex does not incorporate HandBrake source code; it
invokes the HandBrake CLI binary as an external process.

